            <h2>23&#8211;25 March 2027 </h2>           
            <h1>49<sup>th</sup> Generative Linguistics in the Old World (GLOW49)</h1>
            
            <p>Centre of Linguistics of the  University of Lisbon <br>Portugal</p>

            <h2>Call information and more details soon</h2>           


